#: ../../en/publishing.rst:2
msgid "Project Publishing and Documentation"
msgstr "项目发布与文档站点"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:4
msgid "This page documents the release and documentation workflow for repository maintainers."
msgstr "本页面面向维护者，说明当前仓库的发布与文档流程。"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:7
msgid "Version Source"
msgstr "版本来源"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:9
msgid "The package version is stored in two places:"
msgstr "版本号保存在两个地方："

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:11
msgid "``pyproject.toml`` under ``[project].version``."
msgstr "``pyproject.toml`` 的 ``[project].version``。"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:12
msgid "``src/anna_agent/__init__.py`` as ``__version__``."
msgstr "``src/anna_agent/__init__.py`` 中的 ``__version__``。"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:14
msgid "Both values should be updated together before a release."
msgstr "发布前应同步更新这两个值。"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:17
msgid "Build Locally"
msgstr "本地构建"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:26
msgid "PyPI Publishing"
msgstr "PyPI 发布"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:28
msgid "PyPI publishing is not automated by GitHub Actions. The GitHub workflows only build and deploy the documentation site. When a maintainer needs to publish a new package version, build the source and wheel artifacts locally and upload them using the maintainer's PyPI account and local release tooling."
msgstr "PyPI 发布不再由 GitHub Actions 自动执行。当前 GitHub workflows 只负责构建和部署文档站点。维护者需要发布新包版本时，请在本地构建 sdist/wheel，并使用维护者自己的 PyPI 发布流程上传。"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:33
msgid "Recommended tag and release flow:"
msgstr "推荐 tag 与 release 流程："

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:41
msgid "Before uploading to PyPI, verify the package locally with ``uv build`` and check that the version is not already present on PyPI."
msgstr "上传 PyPI 前，请先用 ``uv build`` 在本地验证包，并确认该版本尚未在 PyPI 上存在。"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:45
msgid "GitHub Pages"
msgstr "GitHub Pages"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:47
msgid "The documentation workflow uses the Sphinx i18n/gettext pipeline. English source files live under ``docs/en``. Chinese translations live under ``docs/locale/zh_CN/LC_MESSAGES``. The workflow first rebuilds gettext catalogs, checks that the Chinese catalogs are synchronized, then deploys English pages at the site root and Chinese pages under ``/zh/``. In the repository settings, Pages should use ``GitHub Actions`` as the source."
msgstr "文档 workflow 使用 Sphinx i18n/gettext 流程。英文源文件位于 ``docs/en``，中文翻译位于 ``docs/locale/zh_CN/LC_MESSAGES``。workflow 会先重新生成 gettext catalog，检查中文 catalog 是否同步，然后把英文页面部署到站点根路径，把中文页面部署到 ``/zh/``。仓库设置中 Pages source 应选择 ``GitHub Actions``。"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:53
msgid "Local Documentation Preview"
msgstr "本地预览文档"

#: ../../en/publishing.rst:62
msgid "Then open ``docs/_build/html/index.html`` or ``docs/_build/html/zh/index.html`` in a browser."
msgstr "然后在浏览器中打开 ``docs/_build/html/index.html`` 或 ``docs/_build/html/zh/index.html``。"
